    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, increase the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until the mushrooms start to soften and brown slightly</p>",
      "order": 4,
