      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have started to soften, increase the heat to high and add the<strong> smoky chicken</strong> to the pan</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Cook for a further 4-5 min or until the chicken is beginning to brown</p>",
