    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>reserved</strong> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 6-8 min or until the liquid has reduced by half and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
