    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained</strong> <strong>linguine</strong> to the pan</p><p>Tip: Give it a good stir to release the starch in the pasta and make the sauce naturally creamy</p><p>Before the liquid has fully reduced, remove the linguine from the heat and stir in your<strong> soft cheese </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>smoky chicken & mushroom gluten free linguine</strong></p>",
